OL,4,C'Racist bullying is making my son
OL,5,Cphysically sick'
OL,6, A mother says her 12-year-old son has
OL,7, faced months of racist bullying at
OL,8, school, with a WhatsApp group set up to
OL,9, target him.
OL,11,FMadison Wray said her son was making
OL,12,Fhimself sick every morning before going
OL,13,Fto Aldercar High School in Derbyshire.
OL,15,FShe has contacted police after she said
OL,16,Fstudents threatened to stab him, kicked
OL,17,Fand punched him, and used racist
OL,18,Flanguage towards him.
OL,20,FThe school said it would not tolerate
OL,21,Fbullying and racism.
